tweet_raw: No #FTX victims arent Getting All Their Money Back. I explain why in this weeks Dark Markets news roundup: tinyurl.com/5yevpfweHeres the TLDR:This week saw a wave of headlines claiming FTX will repay customers in full. This is fundamentally misleading.#FTX will repay customers based on the USD value of their crypto on the day of bankruptcy - November 11 2022.
